				<td colspan="2"><span>This link has been passed around several times and i'll use it in this demonstration.
<br />

<br />
http://membres.lycos.fr/Odeus/eqparses/time-rz-0622.html
<br />

<br />
Here you have a fairly typical RZ fight, although a little longer then normal. If you look his overall Damage is 848,862 on the tank in roughly an 8 min fight. Now take 5% of that, that is 42443.1 damage saved in an 8 min fight. We can take this down even further with doing about 1700 dps you're saving the tank from taking 87 damage a second on this song.... There's lots of ways you can break this down, also not to mention that this seems to stack w/ the current &quot;Shielding&quot; cap so like our overhaste its another method that can only be reached by us. I think this is one of our coolest new songs second only to the new charm<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /> I hope to see slight upgrades to this in the future however this is a good starting point.</span></td>
